WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 15]

02:01.000 --> 02:02.180
Kill everyone

02:03.150 --> 02:04.230
but the children.

02:05.510 --> 02:06.130
Don't go there!

02:10.680 --> 02:11.210
Don't go there...

02:12.340 --> 02:16.140
♪Like fleeting shadows, a hundred years slip by♪

02:16.300 --> 02:22.580
♪Let love and hate drift out of sight♪

02:22.940 --> 02:29.420
♪I walk into a heartbreak burning bright♪

02:29.740 --> 02:36.620
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft♪

02:36.700 --> 02:39.820
♪Tears slowly turn to frost♪

02:40.180 --> 02:43.780
♪Fading to white, all is lost♪

02:44.060 --> 02:51.340
♪When I wake, who's by my side?♪

02:56.080 --> 02:57.380
Mother!

03:01.840 --> 03:02.890
Mother!

03:05.750 --> 03:06.500
Mother!

03:08.310 --> 03:08.890
Stop!

03:43.030 --> 03:43.690
You wear painted skins?

03:46.280 --> 03:47.660
You're not from the Shilin Sect.

03:52.030 --> 03:52.940
Who are you exactly?

03:54.430 --> 03:55.340
What are you after?

04:44.310 --> 04:45.220
The Frost Spell.

04:45.920 --> 04:46.660
The Formless Moon Sect.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.250
Wu Wangyan?

05:08.750 --> 05:10.170
You always wanted to know

05:10.870 --> 05:12.580
what secret I was hiding.

05:14.430 --> 05:16.140
Now you have your answer.

05:29.950 --> 05:30.900
The Star Stone...

05:33.070 --> 05:34.010
Give it back!

05:35.890 --> 05:36.610
Dream on.

06:00.240 --> 06:00.810
The sachet...

06:08.880 --> 06:09.560
Oh no!

06:51.000 --> 06:52.340
Threatening me with him won't work.

06:53.560 --> 06:54.870
I can't undo the petrification.

06:56.630 --> 06:57.370
I can't do it.

06:58.070 --> 06:59.300
Then I'll kill him!

07:07.920 --> 07:10.220
The stone thorn has my runes on it.

07:10.920 --> 07:12.100
If I cast the spell...

07:14.000 --> 07:15.420
you'll die instantly.

07:16.720 --> 07:17.860
Do you choose death,

07:19.160 --> 07:20.980
or do you help me free my people?

08:04.070 --> 08:04.660
Qing Yi!

08:23.480 --> 08:24.570
The Dragon Deity's Power.

08:32.720 --> 08:33.890
You have it,

08:35.480 --> 08:37.260
so why no dragon birthmark?

08:39.120 --> 08:39.930
The Dragon clan...

08:42.320 --> 08:43.090
Birthmark...

08:45.870 --> 08:47.420
Your birthmark is so interesting.

08:47.870 --> 08:49.380
It looks like a heart made of flowing water.

08:49.960 --> 08:51.300
How did I never see it?

08:56.200 --> 08:57.380
You're not Wu Wangyan.

08:58.550 --> 08:59.380
You're not her!

09:01.790 --> 09:03.780
You're looking for a child with a dragon birthmark.

09:07.150 --> 09:08.690
Then I know who you are.

09:10.390 --> 09:11.260
That's right.

09:12.630 --> 09:13.810
She's Jiu Ying.

09:35.720 --> 09:36.420
Little Nine.

09:37.630 --> 09:38.330
Or maybe...

09:40.630 --> 09:42.330
I should call you by your true name...

09:46.750 --> 09:47.330
Jiu Ying.

09:58.480 --> 09:59.540
Who sent you here?

10:00.270 --> 10:01.500
Why pretend to be a Shilin Sect member?

10:02.320 --> 10:03.330
It... it's Jiu Ying.

10:03.960 --> 10:05.210
You know of me?

10:06.360 --> 10:07.660
The first time I saw

10:07.660 --> 10:08.810
those nine spots on you,

10:10.550 --> 10:11.780
I suspected it was you.

10:13.440 --> 10:14.870
Those nine markings on your head

10:14.870 --> 10:15.780
are quite pretty.

10:16.510 --> 10:17.780
So I'll call you

10:18.030 --> 10:18.540
Little Nine.

10:19.870 --> 10:20.570
Later,

10:21.440 --> 10:22.660
you found out

10:22.670 --> 10:24.570
we weren't the real Man Man and Di Zhu.

10:25.270 --> 10:26.420
If you were dead,

10:28.000 --> 10:29.610
those two demons

10:30.720 --> 10:31.690
who possess

10:31.690 --> 10:33.300
Man Man and Di Zhu

10:34.480 --> 10:36.210
would never get the Star Stone.

10:37.000 --> 10:38.450
The only one who could stay by us

10:38.450 --> 10:39.780
and eavesdrop on our every word

10:40.600 --> 10:41.420
was Little Nine.

10:42.670 --> 10:43.540
But Little Nine

10:43.960 --> 10:45.020
was just

10:45.030 --> 10:46.690
an ordinary, harmless snake.

10:47.030 --> 10:47.780
Relax.

10:48.720 --> 10:49.690
The blood didn't turn dark.

10:50.790 --> 10:51.330
So,

10:51.440 --> 10:52.970
I had to wait for you to slip up,

10:53.440 --> 10:54.730
to reveal your true form.

10:55.120 --> 10:56.730
I failed twice...

11:12.270 --> 11:12.970
but in the end,

11:13.440 --> 11:14.570
I caught you.

11:15.320 --> 11:16.330
Just a bit too late,

11:17.790 --> 11:19.780
since you've grown your third head.

11:21.670 --> 11:22.810
I don't quite understand

11:23.030 --> 11:24.060
what you're saying.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.380
But it sounds like

11:27.080 --> 11:28.500
you know me well,

11:30.240 --> 11:32.140
like an old friend.

11:33.600 --> 11:34.450
Indeed.

11:36.270 --> 11:37.260
Very well.

11:39.630 --> 11:41.020
All your scheming,

11:42.550 --> 11:43.660
just to get a look

11:43.720 --> 11:44.730
at my true form?

11:45.440 --> 11:46.810
Because in the end,

11:46.840 --> 11:48.500
you'll become the Demon King,

11:49.510 --> 11:50.570
destroying the whole world,

11:51.270 --> 11:52.930
yet no one knows your origin.

11:54.120 --> 11:54.810
So,

11:55.390 --> 11:56.610
I wanted to find out

11:57.670 --> 11:59.520
what exactly you are.

12:03.550 --> 12:04.420
In the beginning,

12:06.120 --> 12:08.060
I was just a snake egg

12:08.320 --> 12:09.270
buried in this earth

12:09.270 --> 12:10.850
for millions of years, unable to hatch.

12:11.960 --> 12:13.540
The egg was filled with deadly venom.

12:14.120 --> 12:16.000
The Aodeng people migrated here

12:16.120 --> 12:17.730
and were poisoned one after another.

12:18.320 --> 12:20.020
They thought it was a plague.

12:22.150 --> 12:24.570
Then the Star Stone fell from the sky,

12:25.550 --> 12:26.610
bringing heavenly fire.

12:31.670 --> 12:32.780
The heat of the flames

12:33.480 --> 12:34.660
hatched you.

12:35.790 --> 12:36.970
I broke out of my shell,

12:37.440 --> 12:39.060
absorbed the Star Stone's power,

12:39.670 --> 12:40.690
and became a demon.

12:41.480 --> 12:42.780
The egg disappeared.

12:43.240 --> 12:44.810
The Aodeng people stopped getting poisoned.

12:45.670 --> 12:46.850
They thought

12:47.870 --> 12:49.690
it was a blessing from the Star Stone.

12:50.960 --> 12:52.140
After I hatched,

12:53.030 --> 12:54.380
the first person I saw

12:56.080 --> 12:57.090
was Di Zhu.

13:08.390 --> 13:10.140
But I was newly born,

13:10.270 --> 13:11.330
my power weak.

13:11.750 --> 13:13.380
I could only take Di Zhu's blood

13:13.720 --> 13:15.060
and briefly possess her.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.330
That way,

13:17.630 --> 13:20.060
I could go into the cave every night

13:20.910 --> 13:22.330
to absorb the Star Stone's power

13:22.960 --> 13:24.020
and grow stronger.

13:25.550 --> 13:27.730
To keep others from getting the Stone,

13:29.200 --> 13:30.380
you started killing.

13:32.000 --> 13:33.300
The Star Stone's power

13:34.030 --> 13:36.210
gave me a second venomous head.

13:37.720 --> 13:39.380
I smeared venom on a hairpin

13:40.080 --> 13:41.900
to kill those who coveted the Stone.

13:42.750 --> 13:44.420
But the venom couldn't kill demons.

13:45.320 --> 13:46.060
So...

13:48.240 --> 13:49.610
I could only frame you.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.140
Too bad,

13:52.630 --> 13:53.660
you didn't succeed.

13:56.360 --> 13:56.970
True.

13:59.480 --> 14:01.610
But I got something unexpected.

14:03.080 --> 14:04.930
I found a power source

14:05.510 --> 14:07.380
even stronger than the Star Stone.

14:08.600 --> 14:09.450
Killing.

14:10.360 --> 14:11.300
No, not killing.

14:12.240 --> 14:13.180
It's fear.

14:14.270 --> 14:15.660
I realized,

14:16.200 --> 14:17.420
the more people died,

14:17.840 --> 14:19.690
the more the Aodeng people feared,

14:20.790 --> 14:22.090
the stronger I became.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.570
In just a few days,

14:29.630 --> 14:31.420
I've already grown my third head.

14:34.360 --> 14:36.020
Even without the Star Stone,

14:37.240 --> 14:39.330
as long as the world is filled with despair,

14:40.670 --> 14:41.500
fear,

14:42.750 --> 14:43.780
and hatred,

14:44.390 --> 14:46.930
I'll have an endless supply of power.

14:47.670 --> 14:48.610
Soon enough,

14:49.790 --> 14:51.180
all nine of my heads

14:52.440 --> 14:53.810
will be fully grown.

14:59.120 --> 15:01.140
With all nine heads,

15:01.720 --> 15:03.320
Jiu Ying can break each head

15:03.320 --> 15:04.690
into nine spirit fragments.

15:05.480 --> 15:07.970
Eighty-one pieces scattered across the world.

15:08.630 --> 15:09.900
That's why this land

15:10.200 --> 15:11.660
is overrun with people

15:12.120 --> 15:13.610
controlled by Jiu Ying.

15:14.320 --> 15:15.660
The Six-Eyed Butterflies under Jiu Ying

15:16.150 --> 15:17.540
planted pupae inside us.

15:18.080 --> 15:19.260
We have no choice but to obey.

15:20.030 --> 15:21.450
Wu Zhiqi was already going to give the Star Stone

15:21.450 --> 15:22.160
to Jiu Ying,

15:22.390 --> 15:24.180
to bring it to the battlefield and destroy humanity.

15:25.120 --> 15:26.210
Why control you

15:27.750 --> 15:29.090
and arrange for us to steal it?

15:31.120 --> 15:31.690
Because...

15:32.910 --> 15:34.660
the Star Stone wasn't meant to destroy humanity.

15:35.480 --> 15:37.090
It was to make humans and demons

15:37.320 --> 15:38.180
destroy each other.

15:38.720 --> 15:39.450
What?

15:41.120 --> 15:42.900
The Yuan Clay Incident,

15:42.910 --> 15:43.690
which sparked the war,

15:44.080 --> 15:44.900
seemed like an accident,

15:45.200 --> 15:46.570
but it was also schemed by Jiu Ying.

15:50.750 --> 15:52.330
You mean Yuan's death

15:54.390 --> 15:55.420
wasn't an accident?

15:56.270 --> 15:57.210
It wasn't just him.

15:58.000 --> 15:59.020
There are countless others

15:59.020 --> 16:00.180
you'd never suspect

16:00.600 --> 16:01.900
possessed by Jiu Ying's spirit.

16:02.390 --> 16:03.500
They walk among us,

16:04.510 --> 16:06.900
constantly stirring conflict between our races,

16:07.200 --> 16:08.450
igniting battles.

16:08.630 --> 16:10.300
And all this strife and hatred

16:11.840 --> 16:13.610
makes Jiu Ying stronger.

16:14.480 --> 16:15.900
She even slaughtered the nine Dragons.

16:18.910 --> 16:20.850
No wonder they say Jiu Ying can't be killed.

16:21.600 --> 16:22.450
Turns out,

16:23.080 --> 16:24.610
even sealed by the nine dragon sons,

16:25.440 --> 16:26.780
you're still causing chaos.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.380
They thought sealing

16:29.390 --> 16:30.780
my nine heads

16:31.320 --> 16:33.260
would destroy me for good.

16:33.870 --> 16:34.730
Too bad

16:35.840 --> 16:37.020
I'd already scattered

16:37.020 --> 16:38.900
countless spirit fragments across the world.

16:39.870 --> 16:41.140
Each piece

16:42.390 --> 16:44.610
can attach to a living being.

16:53.440 --> 16:54.540
Once it attaches,

16:55.150 --> 16:56.260
it waits for a moment

16:56.260 --> 16:57.320
when the host's mind wavers,

16:57.320 --> 16:58.180
then takes control.

16:58.870 --> 17:00.780
As long as one piece remains,

17:01.320 --> 17:02.810
Jiu Ying cannot die.

17:03.150 --> 17:04.380
You might as well give up.

17:05.910 --> 17:06.380
No.

17:06.870 --> 17:07.610
You're wrong.

17:08.750 --> 17:09.650
The Dragon Deity

17:09.720 --> 17:11.410
will defeat Jiu Ying in the end.

17:12.160 --> 17:13.850
All eighty-one spirit fragments

17:14.240 --> 17:15.740
will be destroyed one by one.

17:16.510 --> 17:18.090
That annoying Shilin Sect

17:18.790 --> 17:20.090
has been hunting

17:20.090 --> 17:22.090
for my spirit fragments.

17:22.720 --> 17:24.460
I have to kill Chi Wen,

17:25.160 --> 17:26.500
break the seal,

17:28.070 --> 17:29.610
and get my heads back.

17:30.830 --> 17:32.690
So you've been searching

17:32.690 --> 17:33.700
for the dragon's descendants.

17:35.070 --> 17:36.810
Because only a dragon...

17:37.790 --> 17:38.610
Can kill a dragon.

17:44.880 --> 17:46.500
The Six-Eyed Butterflies gave us the glowing worm.

17:47.720 --> 17:50.090
Once it's inside the Star Stone,

17:50.400 --> 17:51.510
it will devour

17:51.510 --> 17:53.130
his insides,

17:53.480 --> 17:54.940
make him lose control,

17:55.400 --> 17:56.700
and cause an explosion.

18:13.000 --> 18:13.850
Where's the Star Stone?

18:38.680 --> 18:39.810
What do we do now?

18:40.480 --> 18:41.300
Where are we taking him?

18:42.030 --> 18:42.850
We can't go anywhere.

18:59.880 --> 19:00.700
The Six-Eyed Butterfly...

19:02.680 --> 19:03.700
is actually two people.

19:04.240 --> 19:04.980
That's right.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.300
Unlike you,

19:06.680 --> 19:08.410
we're inseparable,

19:08.790 --> 19:10.780
loving brothers.

19:21.270 --> 19:21.780
Watch out!

19:31.000 --> 19:31.740
You've got it wrong.

19:32.550 --> 19:33.740
We're not with him.

19:34.310 --> 19:35.410
Threatening us with him

19:35.960 --> 19:36.540
won't work.

19:37.000 --> 19:38.130
You should just kill him.

19:39.830 --> 19:40.650
Are you sure?

19:41.640 --> 19:43.300
The look on the person behind you

19:43.590 --> 19:44.980
says otherwise.

19:46.310 --> 19:47.610
If you don't want him dead,

19:47.830 --> 19:48.780
come with us.

20:00.240 --> 20:00.810
Don't forget

20:02.070 --> 20:03.780
he imprisoned you for all those years.

20:06.480 --> 20:07.570
You said earlier

20:08.480 --> 20:10.260
he secretly helped us

20:11.310 --> 20:12.410
by letting me go.

20:17.070 --> 20:18.130
All these years,

20:19.510 --> 20:20.700
in that tiny space,

20:21.400 --> 20:23.130
he was my only friend.

20:33.160 --> 20:34.890
If you no longer care about the Star Stone,

20:35.750 --> 20:37.130
then why did you attack me

20:37.160 --> 20:37.890
at the wedding?

20:47.640 --> 20:51.540
- Kiss! - Kiss!

20:58.110 --> 20:59.060
Come out, Little Nine!

21:00.030 --> 21:01.410
I simply wanted you dead.

21:17.400 --> 21:18.020
Tian Di!

21:33.440 --> 21:34.410
Let Wu Zhiqi go!

21:34.640 --> 21:35.260
Stop!

22:01.830 --> 22:03.460
You're covered in wounds,

22:04.200 --> 22:05.850
yet you can't bear to hurt her.

22:06.640 --> 22:07.740
How devoted.

22:08.750 --> 22:09.940
Let's see

22:11.270 --> 22:12.780
how long you can last.

22:20.660 --> 22:22.500
♪One winter day♪

22:23.180 --> 22:28.140
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes♪

22:28.860 --> 22:36.340
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by♪

22:36.420 --> 22:43.820
♪The wind asked why he smiled in silence♪

22:44.220 --> 22:50.580
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart♪

23:16.160 --> 23:16.740
Don't be rash!

23:25.640 --> 23:26.090
Oh no.

23:26.480 --> 23:27.540
He's losing control of his power!

23:38.830 --> 23:39.330
Tian Di...

23:39.790 --> 23:40.330
No!

23:44.400 --> 23:45.020
Yuan Xizai!

24:17.070 --> 24:19.170
So this is the Star Stone exit Master Bai Ze mentioned?

24:19.680 --> 24:20.540
This stone tablet?

24:21.590 --> 24:22.810
It's Wu Shiguang's master's grave.

24:23.160 --> 24:23.850
Stop bickering.

24:24.440 --> 24:25.170
Quick, smear the blood.

24:25.400 --> 24:26.260
Okay. Got it.

24:26.920 --> 24:28.060
Wu Shiguang would be surprised

24:28.510 --> 24:29.780
that the keepsake of our friendship I kept

24:30.000 --> 24:31.300
would save his life years later.

25:00.310 --> 25:01.460
Why isn't it working?

25:02.510 --> 25:03.780
That liar Bai Ze!

25:07.070 --> 25:07.880
Are they really going to die

25:07.880 --> 25:08.940
in the disasters?

25:40.310 --> 25:40.890
Master...

25:41.640 --> 25:42.740
What's happening?

25:43.200 --> 25:44.170
Father!

25:45.830 --> 25:46.780
Mother!

25:47.030 --> 25:47.540
Shiguang!

26:05.680 --> 26:07.650
Quick, take him and go!

26:08.000 --> 26:08.740
I won't!

26:09.030 --> 26:10.370
I have to save my parents!

26:10.830 --> 26:11.260
Father!

26:28.640 --> 26:29.410
What are you waiting for?

26:29.550 --> 26:30.090
Go after them!

28:20.270 --> 28:20.810
Lu Wuyi!

28:23.860 --> 28:26.140
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

28:27.550 --> 28:28.090
Lu Wuyi!

28:44.200 --> 28:44.650
Oh no.

28:44.680 --> 28:45.740
What's happening to Wu Zhiqi?

28:46.790 --> 28:47.650
The third head,

28:48.270 --> 28:49.400
the head of frenzy.

28:49.690 --> 28:51.280
It drives a person mad,

28:51.790 --> 28:52.740
making their demon power run wild.

28:56.960 --> 28:58.090
If Wu Zhiqi loses control,

28:58.720 --> 29:00.160
it'll cause the Hurricane Catastrophe.

29:02.510 --> 29:03.300
I've figured out

29:03.310 --> 29:04.060
Jiu Ying's origin.

29:04.250 --> 29:04.850
Let's go.

29:05.000 --> 29:06.090
We'll use the Star Stone to leave.

29:07.440 --> 29:08.130
- Okay. - Let's go.

29:10.000 --> 29:10.700
Where's the Star Stone?

29:27.200 --> 29:27.850
You go first.

29:28.590 --> 29:30.090
You can turn into sand and leave.

29:32.400 --> 29:32.980
Let's go together!

30:20.720 --> 30:22.130
Once we get the Star Stone,

30:22.750 --> 30:23.890
we can use our power

30:24.350 --> 30:25.700
to leave the illusion.

30:52.680 --> 30:53.220
You...

31:00.110 --> 31:00.650
He...

31:02.830 --> 31:03.980
He's Yuan Wuhuo,

31:05.440 --> 31:06.370
the butterfly demon.

31:08.160 --> 31:08.940
He went in too?

31:10.200 --> 31:11.500
When the Star Stone's pull

31:11.500 --> 31:12.810
was strongest earlier,

31:13.510 --> 31:15.060
I almost got sucked in.

31:23.720 --> 31:25.060
The butterfly demon hiding in the shadows

31:25.060 --> 31:25.940
pushed me away.

31:26.960 --> 31:28.850
But he got pulled in himself.

31:30.440 --> 31:31.170
So,

31:31.830 --> 31:33.500
in the past they're living in,

31:35.680 --> 31:36.330
who is the true owner

31:36.350 --> 31:37.650
of that time?

31:38.310 --> 31:39.260
That past

31:40.160 --> 31:41.300
was shared

31:41.300 --> 31:42.810
by the two brothers.

31:43.270 --> 31:44.260
They are both the owners,

31:45.070 --> 31:46.330
and witnesses to each other.

31:48.920 --> 31:50.370
You're not Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "free of misfortune"]

31:51.680 --> 31:53.460
You're the butterfly demon, Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing"]

31:55.160 --> 31:55.650
That's right.

31:57.920 --> 31:59.500
So you've been acting this whole time.

32:01.750 --> 32:02.410
That's right.

32:03.440 --> 32:05.220
How else could I make you lower your guard,

32:05.830 --> 32:07.370
help me get the Star Stone,

32:08.350 --> 32:09.330
and leave this place?

32:11.160 --> 32:13.130
So you were behind it before too.

32:15.200 --> 32:15.780
Exactly.

32:17.640 --> 32:19.330
I tried to kill Tian Di

32:20.920 --> 32:22.740
to turn him back into the Star Stone.

32:23.550 --> 32:24.570
But it didn't work.

32:25.720 --> 32:27.130
All that struggling

32:28.070 --> 32:29.540
was pointless.

32:51.720 --> 32:53.260
Did you really think

32:55.160 --> 32:56.370
I was your brother?

32:58.440 --> 32:59.220
Aren't you?

33:00.680 --> 33:01.330
No.

33:04.160 --> 33:06.170
Then why do you look exactly like me?

33:07.590 --> 33:08.540
You're wrong.

33:11.590 --> 33:13.060
Know your place.

33:14.590 --> 33:16.780
You look like me.

33:18.550 --> 33:19.130
I...

33:19.820 --> 33:23.140
♪Who paints the moon in light of day?♪

33:23.660 --> 33:27.660
♪In silver glow, I'm black and white...♪

33:27.680 --> 33:29.330
Who am I?

33:32.000 --> 33:33.780
You'll never know.

33:33.940 --> 33:38.100
♪Tell me why these hands won't let go...♪

33:38.110 --> 33:39.890
Stay here forever.

33:41.100 --> 33:42.540
♪Black and white, they say♪

33:42.980 --> 33:45.700
♪Love and hate just twist and fade♪

33:46.140 --> 33:47.580
♪All these words we write♪

33:47.940 --> 33:51.140
♪Still can't show my shade♪

33:51.380 --> 33:53.620
♪Whose regret♪

33:53.900 --> 33:56.100
♪Calls out my name?♪

33:56.460 --> 34:01.020
♪Chasing shadows, I slip away♪

34:02.300 --> 34:05.540
♪Who would turn their vows to bitter wine?♪

34:06.140 --> 34:10.300
♪An aging hero holds the falling light♪

34:11.780 --> 34:16.260
♪One last beat, one spark, one burning fire♪

34:16.420 --> 34:21.020
♪See the night ignite in flame♪

34:21.100 --> 34:22.700
♪Black and white, they say♪

34:23.020 --> 34:25.820
♪Rivers run and drift away...♪

34:26.440 --> 34:27.540
Yuan Xizai!

34:27.980 --> 34:31.140
♪Then just fade away♪

34:31.380 --> 34:33.620
♪If I cross that line♪

34:33.900 --> 34:36.140
♪Past the hills of time...♪

34:36.440 --> 34:37.500
Why did I lose my power?

34:37.880 --> 34:38.940
Quick, heal him!

34:39.440 --> 34:39.940
Hurry!

34:40.800 --> 34:41.250
Xizai!

34:41.550 --> 34:42.020
Xizai!

34:43.360 --> 34:43.940
Save him!

34:44.670 --> 34:45.420
Save him!

34:46.460 --> 34:51.940
♪I just need you to remember me♪

35:00.710 --> 35:01.570
I can't hold it together much longer.

35:02.550 --> 35:03.940
The Star Stone must not shatter.

35:04.840 --> 35:06.380
I still need it to save my people.

35:07.000 --> 35:08.020
Is there any way?

35:09.150 --> 35:09.570
Yes.

35:10.400 --> 35:10.980
What is it?

35:13.510 --> 35:14.170
What is it?

35:15.110 --> 35:15.940
The Dragon Deity's Power.

35:17.280 --> 35:18.420
It can restore anything,

35:19.070 --> 35:20.170
and bring the dead back to life.

35:30.400 --> 35:31.460
Dragon hearts as one,

35:32.800 --> 35:33.860
all to source return,

35:35.760 --> 35:36.860
all barriers break!

36:10.760 --> 36:11.900
Dragon hearts as one,

36:13.150 --> 36:14.170
all to source return,

36:15.280 --> 36:16.380
all barriers break!

36:48.550 --> 36:49.690
Master Jiu Ying truly has

36:50.070 --> 36:51.500
flawless foresight.

36:56.190 --> 36:58.090
I infused my demonic energy

36:58.230 --> 36:59.730
into a fragment of the Star Stone.

37:00.710 --> 37:03.540
Once it joins with the piece Wu Zhiqi has,

37:04.190 --> 37:05.530
the entire Star Stone

37:05.920 --> 37:07.540
will shatter completely.

37:09.360 --> 37:11.770
Wu Zhiqi will surely sacrifice himself,

37:12.280 --> 37:14.650
releasing the Dragon Deity's Power to fix it.

37:15.360 --> 37:17.900
Then you'll have your chance to seize his power.

37:57.630 --> 37:58.820
Give up.

37:59.630 --> 38:01.210
Take after Xiaowei,

38:02.550 --> 38:04.060
and you'll share her fate.

38:20.070 --> 38:20.860
Bai Ze,

38:21.360 --> 38:23.420
you already gave seventy percent of your power

38:23.800 --> 38:25.650
to that false Dragon Deity.

38:26.320 --> 38:27.860
And you used another twenty percent

38:28.150 --> 38:29.770
to fix the Star Stone.

38:30.760 --> 38:32.420
With the ten percent left,

38:33.190 --> 38:34.770
you want to break my barrier?

38:35.480 --> 38:37.090
What a joke.

38:41.150 --> 38:42.020
Or maybe...

38:45.070 --> 38:46.020
you could try

38:46.030 --> 38:47.690
using the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:07.440 --> 39:08.730
Now we're really trapped here.

39:09.630 --> 39:10.500
It's all my fault.

39:11.800 --> 39:12.570
It's all my fault.

39:13.550 --> 39:14.210
I'm sorry.

39:16.880 --> 39:18.570
At least we know Jiu Ying's origin,

39:19.400 --> 39:20.340
that's something.

39:21.190 --> 39:22.420
And we found out something else,

39:24.360 --> 39:25.130
even better.

39:25.840 --> 39:26.460
What's it?

39:27.670 --> 39:28.420
Jiu Ying's weakness.

39:30.880 --> 39:31.940
What's his weakness?

39:33.440 --> 39:34.860
The same weakness as mine.

39:38.510 --> 39:39.020
Look out!

39:42.230 --> 39:42.820
Ji Ling!

39:43.710 --> 39:44.250
Ji Ling!

39:47.190 --> 39:47.690
Ji Ling!

39:48.230 --> 39:49.060
Hold on to me!

39:49.710 --> 39:50.610
Don't let go!

39:54.480 --> 39:55.090
Lu Wuyi!

40:00.960 --> 40:01.690
What are you doing?

40:05.960 --> 40:06.900
A spike will help...

40:11.420 --> 40:13.340
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

40:15.820 --> 40:17.740
♪Through a thousand shadows...♪

40:19.320 --> 40:20.980
When disaster strikes,

40:21.550 --> 40:24.020
lovers stay together.

40:27.070 --> 40:28.090
"Live together, die together"?

40:28.590 --> 40:30.290
That's just a story to fool girls.

40:31.030 --> 40:32.250
I don't like him

40:33.000 --> 40:34.020
enough

40:34.020 --> 40:35.100
to die for him.

40:35.100 --> 40:42.900
♪I'll always stay with you♪

40:43.780 --> 40:46.180
♪Don't be sad...♪

40:46.760 --> 40:47.500
The Star Stone!

40:48.180 --> 40:50.580
♪Don't you cry♪

40:50.620 --> 40:52.460
♪Through the darkest nights...♪

40:52.550 --> 40:53.170
Let go!

40:54.360 --> 40:54.940
No!

40:55.800 --> 40:57.130
Let go of the other hand!

40:57.920 --> 40:58.980
Take out the spike!

40:59.670 --> 41:00.500
Trust me!

41:01.300 --> 41:03.660
♪Don't be sad♪

41:03.700 --> 41:05.500
♪Through a thousand broken lights...♪

41:07.230 --> 41:07.900
Let's take a gamble.

41:09.400 --> 41:10.940
If we lose, we just stay here.

41:12.630 --> 41:13.730
And I'll marry you!

41:16.180 --> 41:18.020
♪Stay with you♪

41:19.580 --> 41:23.580
♪See the daylight wrapped in silver light♪

41:24.620 --> 41:27.460
♪Black turns white with time passing by♪

41:28.060 --> 41:32.780
♪She holds a flower, counts the seasons slow♪

41:33.260 --> 41:35.740
♪Waiting for stone to bloom♪

41:36.180 --> 41:40.060
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

41:40.620 --> 41:44.540
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

41:44.940 --> 41:47.900
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

41:48.780 --> 41:53.180
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

41:53.700 --> 41:57.460
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

41:58.140 --> 42:01.820
♪Your sunrise fades into my gray♪

42:02.380 --> 42:05.700
♪You left behind your final words♪

42:06.100 --> 42:10.620
♪And every word became a scar♪

42:11.060 --> 42:14.860
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

42:15.500 --> 42:19.500
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

42:19.820 --> 42:22.860
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

42:23.700 --> 42:28.100
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

42:28.460 --> 42:32.420
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

42:32.940 --> 42:36.780
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

42:37.300 --> 42:40.860
♪I call for you, my only one♪

42:41.340 --> 42:48.660
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

42:49.510 --> 42:50.210
You're here.

43:29.740 --> 43:30.900
♪It's your light♪

43:31.100 --> 43:32.980
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:33.140 --> 43:36.260
♪That set the night alight♪

43:36.620 --> 43:43.140
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:44.900 --> 43:46.780
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:47.220 --> 43:51.660
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:52.460 --> 43:54.140
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:54.300 --> 43:59.700
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

44:00.460 --> 44:05.860
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:08.180 --> 44:14.220
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

44:15.180 --> 44:17.340
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

44:17.620 --> 44:22.460
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

44:22.820 --> 44:25.140
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

44:25.340 --> 44:30.420
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

44:30.660 --> 44:32.660
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:32.940 --> 44:37.300
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:38.300 --> 44:45.260
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

45:01.820 --> 45:04.780
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:05.860 --> 45:09.260
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:10.060 --> 45:12.580
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

45:12.820 --> 45:15.900
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

45:16.300 --> 45:18.620
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

45:19.140 --> 45:23.540
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

45:23.780 --> 45:25.940
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

45:26.340 --> 45:31.300
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

45:31.540 --> 45:32.700
♪It's your light♪

45:32.900 --> 45:34.740
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:34.940 --> 45:38.060
♪That set the night alight♪

45:38.820 --> 45:48.260
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
